latestPosts.caption:
My MasterChef journey is the most beautiful chapter of my life When I got selected for MasterChef India it felt like my dream have come true from dreaming of becoming a part of MasterChef India to being there .My MasterChef journey have been a rollercoaster ride i had some ups and some down but the most important thing was I never gave up . Being the Part of MasterChef family was such a great great experience. Working under the guidance of such great chefs @ranveer.brar @vikaskhannagroup and @arorgarima and making sweet memories with my other homecooks. This chapter of my life have changed my life and I will  always be grateful to my judges for giving me this opportunity and also getting recognised as kamaldeep [KDK] and also [KAMAALDEEP]
which was given by Chef VIKAS KHANNA 

From being selected for MasterChef India to getting my Name apron and then IMMUNITY PIN and the most amazing one being the FIRST FINALIST  of MasterChef India this journey was the best part and after that the TOP5 CONTESTANT 

And thanks to everyone who supported me and now let's start a new Food Journey with me where I will be Sharing some cool recipes with u all .

Love,
KDK
